title.$t: Mindcrack Fan Server Clash - UHC - Ep. 5

content.$t:
Welcome to the first battle of the Server Clash series. This series puts two servers against each other in a battle to the death... or other objectives based on the game type:
 
This time we will be playing Ultra Hardcore, a Minecraft mod that turns off health regeneration. The only way to get back health is with a golden apple or health potions. The recipes for golden apples have also changed to require ingots instead of nuggets. Our two teams will battle to see the last one standing.
 
Mindcrack Reddit Server:
 
AudicyMC: http://www.youtube.com/user/audicymc
 
ghowden: http://www.youtube.com/user/Eluinhost
 
Fairyjuice: http://www.youtube.com/user/Entropiestromstaerke
 
sonmica: http://www.youtube.com/user/sonmicaLP
 
Mindcrack Fan Server:

Arrowheadcobra: http://www.youtube.com/user/ArrowhoodCobra
 
Atomic2354: http://www.youtube.com/user/atomic2354
 
Uisdead99: http://www.youtube.com/user/uisdead99
 
 
Intro by: sonmica ( http://www.youtube.com/user/sonmicaLP )
